{"tid":1503571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"9月1日開學重點","createTime":"2019-08-25T04:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T12:59:24.000Z","uid":283919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de725147fa5a1e9e90d4b4efc8cacbe85dda36c6","tid":1503571,"uid":283919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"我見好多Post都話要點點點泡製狗仔狗女，但你如果欺凌佢只係發洩到你一時之恨，為長遠計，千其唔好欺凌佢地，反而要招攬佢地！<br />\n<br />\n對住狗仔女我地應該：<br />\nD狗公已經日日出去同我地對抗，冇時間陪狗仔狗女，我地要更加關心佢地，將佢地變做自己人，返學日日反洗腦行動，一個人洗佢地唔到，就十個人洗，十個都洗唔到就全班洗，約埋佢地出去發夢現佢地狗爸，內部爆破佢地！<br />\n<br />\n對住狗嫂應該：<br />\n有冇Ex依家做左狗嫂呀？佢地呢排老公冇人陪，一場相識，你有冇關心下人地丫？得閒約人出黎聚下舊、飲飲野啦，其他自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要對付卑鄙既人！<br />\n一定要比佢地更卑鄙！"},{"pid":"44a7e3056c46c22b9abec520ae118ab7bc9f82c9","tid":1503571,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:24:33.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54d6d0aa07ba66a1c70845c1a0ab8c7e333c456d","tid":1503571,"uid":283919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:24:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"904faecb4f1e50b74a30c2802cbca70db9a34981","tid":1503571,"uid":283919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cdd2d06307e4336313aa7ebaeac9f2913d69a40","tid":1503571,"uid":283919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72ef7c7467d917f6c0202ed1b7965f1310d6a7cf","tid":1503571,"uid":283919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f9ddcaff2fd818e37bf0cc97a011b89f861365c","tid":1503571,"uid":283919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"推"}]}